parameters: Clea: They are definitely dead, it's our victory...
Clea: We finally did it... We defeated the dragon!
Thief Nora: We did it! Finally, ugh, I'm so relieved!
アトゥ　アゴにあ　セリス
General Atu: Are you all safe? What happened to the dragon!?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, we did it! It's a victory for
everyone who participated in the battle!

Guild Leader Agonia: Now we can finally breathe a sigh of
relief... The goblins will also lose their leadership with
this.

Guild Leader Agonia: Contact the nearby village... Celis, is
something wrong?

Mage Relm: Clea-san, what are you doing!? The dragon is
already dead, it's okay!

Mage Relm: Nora-san, please help me! If we leave it like
this, the dragon's eyes might break too!

Thief Nora: O-Please calm down! If you swing your sword like
that, Clea-san might get hurt too!

Priestess Sophia: Clea-chan, please calm down. The revenge
is over, everything should be fine now--

Clea: It's not over! My revenge is not over! Nothing has
been resolved!

Clea: Haa...haa... It's not over, isn't that strange... This
is absurd.
Clea: Why don't I have a father or a mother!?

Clea: We defeated the dragon, right!? It's dead... so why
isn't it coming back!

Clea: I've done it! No matter how tough it was, no matter
how painful it was, and yet, why!?

Clea: Whether it's magic or a miracle, please bring back my
father and mother!

Clea: We defeated the dragon, right!? It's not strange for
something like that to happen, right--

Guild Leader Agonia: Clea... Listen carefully. There is no
magic or miracle that can bring people back to life.

Guild Leader Agonia: You came here for revenge, and you
won't gain anything else here.

Clea: Ahaha... I know that... but... there might still be
something that could happen... up until now...
Clea: Why... why did I defeat the dragon... I... I...
Imperial Soldier: The dragon has fallen! We did it, we won!
General Atu: You guys! Right now--

Imperial Soldiers: Praise the heroes who defeated the
dragon! Hail the Dragon Slayers! Hail the adventurer Clea!

Imperial Soldiers: The hero of the empire! The reincarnation
of a hero! Hail the Dragon Slayers! Hail the adventurer
Clea!

Imperial Soldiers: The daughter has avenged her slain
parents! Hail the Dragon Slayer! Hail the adventurer Clea!
